sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant F as Frontend
  participant G as Gateway
  participant US as User Service
  participant DB as PostgreSQL
  participant AN as Analytics Service

  U->>F: Sign in via OAuth
  F->>G: POST /api/users/me
  G->>US: create or upsert user
  US->>DB: insert User + defaults
  US->>AN: emit USER_CREATED event
  AN-->>US: ack
  US-->>F: user profile payload

  F->>G: GET /api/users/me
  G->>US: fetch profile
  US->>DB: query User + Preferences + Stats
  US-->>F: hydrated user state
